Package: ICPSurv
Type: Package
Title: Invariant Causal Prediction for Survival Data
Version: 0.1
Author: Anna Laksafoss
Maintainer: Anna Laksafoss <vbs190@alumni.ku.dk>
Description: Methods for estimation of causal predictors and identification of 
    invariant models for a target variable. Using heterogeneous data from 
    different (possibly unknown) environments the methods identify invariant 
    models and use these to make causal inference. The methods are suited for 
    target variables that may be described by a linear, generalized linear or 
    hazard model. 
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
License: GPL
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    survival (>= 2.41-3),
    timereg (>= 1.9.2),
    fda (>= 2.4.8)
Suggests: 
    ggplot2 (>= 3.1.0),
    testthat,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
RoxygenNote: 7.0.0
VignetteBuilder: knitr
